Command line tool for Language Translation Using Microsoft Translational Api.
======================================================================================

Function Supported:
==================

1) Detect Language.
2) Translate a given Text to other language.
3) Identify Number of Sentences and words in a Given paragraph.

Dependencies:
=============

1. Python-requests
2. BeautifulSoup

Installation:
============:
1) Fill you your client id and client secret in the credential file.(https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/hh454950.aspx)
2) Run the Script from Command line.
